    // The host launches with global_work = blk * BLOCK_SIZE.
    // global_id ranges from 0 to blk*BLOCK_SIZE - 1.
    // We map global_id to the specific row index within the current block set.
    // In the original code: elem_19 ranges from 0 to blk-1.
    // Each thread handles one elem_19.
